# Testing

Follow `ai-framework/standards/testing-rules.md`.

- Unit tests: `Code/{{AREA}}/{{MODULE}}/test/`
- Test cases: `Test/{{AREA}}/test-cases/TC-XXXX`
- Record test commands in validation report evidence

Add or update tests for behaviour changes. Do not mark tasks complete with failing required tests.
